<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Alumni Network</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/landing.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to BridgeU!</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to the Alumni Network</h1>
        <p>Connecting former students with opportunities, resources, and each other.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Networking</h2>
            <p>Connect with fellow alumni and expand your professional network.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Resources</h2>
            <p>Access valuable resources and tools for career development.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Events</h2>
            <p>Stay updated on upcoming alumni events and reunions.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="donation">
        <h2>Donation</h2>
        <p>Support the network by contributing to our fund for alumni projects and scholarships.</p>
        <button onclick="window.location.href='/donation'">Donate Now</button>
    </section>

    <section class="job-portal">
        <h2>Job Portal</h2>
        <p>Browse job listings and career opportunities specifically for alumni.</p>
        <button onclick="window.location.href='/job-portal'">Explore Jobs</button>
    </section>

    <section class="forum">
        <h2>Forum</h2>
        <p>Join discussions, ask questions, and share insights with other alumni in our forum.</p>
        <button onclick="window.location.href='/forum'">Visit Forum</button>
    </section>

    <section class="followers">
        <h2>Followers</h2>
        <p>View and connect with alumni who follow you or have similar interests.</p>
        <button onclick="window.location.href='/followers'">See Followers</button>
    </section>

    <section class="following">
        <h2>Following</h2>
        <p>Manage your connections and see the updates from alumni you follow.</p>
        <button onclick="window.location.href='/following'">See Following</button>
    </section>

    <section class="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or need support, feel free to reach out to us.</p>
        <button onclick="window.location.href='/contact'">Contact Us</button>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 BridgeU. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
